messages.message: Hey there peeps :wave: I've been working on some changes to bring sandbox template definitions into the repo (so we have things like change logs, reverts, checks, etc available to us) and wanted to solicit some feedback on this initial PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/65457) I have for it. I'm specifically looking for approvals/rejections from @mfichman and @Cody Boggs, however I would love to hear from anyone who is interested! (This also introduces cue (https://cuelang.org/docs/introduction/) to the stack, so on the off chance anyone here has prior exposure I would love your feedback as well!)
